But she's really perfect for this cosmetics promotion.

00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:12.100
The beauty products Emma introduced during her livestream

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.740
are well-known among all young women.

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:14.500
Thank you, Keishi.

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:15.280
Yes.

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:17.850
I didn't expect you to know so much about this.

00:00:17.850 --> 00:00:21.300
