on the client's side changed.

00:00:36.090 --> 00:00:38.100
I heard it's a newly appointed section chief…

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:41.830
Got it.

00:00:41.830 --> 00:00:43.300
I'll be joining as well.

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:45.800
- Thank you so much.
- Thanks, that really puts my mind at ease.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:48.500
Alright! We absolutely have to nail this project!

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.300
- Thank you.
- We'll head out now.

00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:57.020
