who was two years ahead of me.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:08.220
Really?

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:09.610
Long time no see.

00:03:09.810 --> 00:03:11.100
It's really been a long time.

00:03:11.100 --> 00:03:12.760
Did you get a little taller?

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:16.650
- No way, senpai.
- I think there's probably someone out there who's a better match for Keishi.

00:03:16.650 --> 00:03:17.700
It's really been a long time.

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:19.150
You haven't changed at all.

00:03:19.150 --> 00:03:20.500
I was really surprised.

00:03:20.500 --> 00:03:25.500
Plus, Keishi is even younger than me,
