00:03:25.870 --> 00:03:27.360
Has everyone already seen it?

00:03:27.500 --> 00:03:30.800
Even I love that makeup product so much myself.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:33.740
I seriously want to recommend it to everyone!

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:39.300
Btw, I didn't expect you guys to be senior
and junior in school. What a coincidence!

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:41.540
