00:04:02.900 --> 00:04:05.500
I actually use your company's face masks myself, too.

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:06.700
Thank you.

00:04:06.700 --> 00:04:09.200
Putting in consistent effort every day really does matter.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.200
Yeah, that's right.

