00:04:21.960 --> 00:04:23.000
Your skin looks great.

00:04:23.100 --> 00:04:24.650
Not at all. I actually take care of it every single day.

00:04:24.650 --> 00:04:26.500
Huh? But you're 30…?

00:04:26.500 --> 00:04:27.500
I'm 32 this year.

00:04:27.570 --> 00:04:31.030
Oh wow, Emma-chan is really adorable.

00:04:31.230 --> 00:04:33.260
Tojo-san, thank you as well for helping to follow up.

00:04:33.500 --> 00:04:35.120
It's great that the promotional plans were finalized smoothly.

00:04:35.170 --> 00:04:36.200
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:04:36.690 --> 00:04:39.210
