00:05:13.700 --> 00:05:14.500
The two of us together.

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:20.800
Sure, I don't have anything urgent going on anyway.

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:23.400
Then I'll go ahead and tell them.

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:27.300
Sure.

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:30.600
No problem.

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:33.400
No, that would be going too far.

00:05:37.700 --> 00:05:39.200
Hey, bro, you're back!

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:42.000
