00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:35.600
Is it really okay to just leave it like this,

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:37.200
Suzume-chan?

00:06:39.700 --> 00:06:42.000
Tojo-san, the next meeting with Miss Emma

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.600
