00:06:46.100 --> 00:06:47.620
Sakuma-san is okay with it, right?

00:06:47.620 --> 00:06:48.300
Yes.

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:50.160
He agreed right away, saying he'd go to the sauna
with Keishi while he's at it.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.200
Alright, that's enough.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:53.800
I see.

00:06:54.170 --> 00:06:57.420
Sorry to trouble you on your day off. Thanks so much.

00:06:57.420 --> 00:06:59.000
- Okay.
- Alright, I'll head out first.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.800
I'll get in touch with Sakuma-san.

00:07:01.030 --> 00:07:01.800
Okay.

00:07:11.210 --> 00:07:12.400
Thanks for your hard work.

