Folded so neatly!

00:09:23.260 --> 00:09:23.880
Huh?

00:09:25.400 --> 00:09:26.000
Wow, that's amazing!

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.000
It sticks to your hands.

00:09:33.700 --> 00:09:35.360
Which side is the front and which is the back?

00:09:35.460 --> 00:09:37.700
Suzume-chan, let's get pretty together!

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.000
Yay!

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:45.800
Yeah, that's right! Right over there!

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:48.000
Thank you.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.860
Amazing!

