00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:34.600
- Oh! Hey, you're back!
- Yeah, I'm back.

00:21:40.800 --> 00:21:42.000
Never have I realized...

00:21:42.600 --> 00:21:44.600
the world could be such a beautiful place.

00:21:58.500 --> 00:22:00.300
I'm also really looking forward to next time.

